title: Rosie O'Donnell will rally with liberals outside White House | Washington Examiner
text:
Longtime Trump nemesis Rosie O'Donnell plans to join forces with several liberal groups at a rally outside the White House on Tuesday to protest President Trump's "harmful agenda."
Organizers are calling the protest "A Resistance Address: Defending American Values in a Time of Moral Crisis." O'Donnell, a liberal comedian, will be among the protesters who will be participating in this event, according to a statement.
The protest comes the same day the president will be addressing Congress for the first time.
O'Donnell and Trump have sparred for years. Trump famously called the actress a "pig" and she retaliated by calling him "mentally unstable."
